Journal.Title: Zhongguo Zhong yao za zhi = Zhongguo zhongyao zazhi = China journal of Chinese materia medica

AbstractText: By the fourth survey of Chinese medicinal resources, new medicinal plants records of 1 family, 2 genera and 6 species were reported in Chongqing.They are Annonaceae, Fissistigma, Monochasma, Sophora tonkinensis, Fissistigma retusum, Monochasma sheareri, Primula ranunculoids, Chirita pinnatifida and Hylotelephium sieboldii.All the voucher specimens are preserved in Herbarium of Chongqing Institute of Medicinal Plant Cultivation.
